divs: Sighting DetailsMy father and aunt were out taking pictures of the country side for my aunt to make into a painting. They snap two quick picks of a nice looking spot by a small lake called Mud Lake. When they looked at the pictures, they saw a large spherical reddish blob and a smaller blue orb just beneath it.
Summary: two photos taken, but photographers didn't notice the objects when taken
